title: USA Compression Partners Breaks Below 200-Day Moving Average - Notable for USAC - Nasdaq.com
text: In trading on Tuesday, shares of USA Compression Partners LP (Symbol: USAC) crossed below their 200 day moving average of $16.03, changing hands as low as $16.01 per share. USA Compression Partners LP shares are currently trading down about 5.5% on the day. The chart below shows the one year performance of USAC shares, versus its 200 day moving average:     Looking at the chart above, USAC's low point in its 52 week range is $12.085 per share, with $19 as the 52 week high point - that compares with a last trade of $16.04.
